My overall assessment

Based on everything we've designed across this series, ARTH.OS is no longer just an ERP concept. It is the blueprint for an AI-native enterprise operating system.

The biggest risk is no longer a lack of ideasвЂ”it's execution complexity. Success will depend on disciplined delivery, a small number of exceptional production modules first, and a platform architecture that stays clean as the product grows. That focus will do far more for ARTH.OS than continuing to expand the architectural surface area.